comments: Best band director I have ever had so far, most likely best ever, he is an encyclopedia on everything! Just simply amazing.

Will forget about all the hard work and sacrifices you\'ve made for the group or will just take all the credit for it. Teaches technique well but will go on long-winded tangents. Will only reward students whose parents make routine contributions or who are popular/well-liked in the group, thereby depriving them of reaching their hopes and dreams.

This guy can teach you how to play ANYTHING. If you\'re willing to practice every day, he has all the necessary tools to make you sound GREAT. Highly recommended if you\'re interested in playing music, classical or jazz.
